text.section:
A person may not possess, own, carry, or transport a firearm if that person has been convicted of:
a felony under this title;
a crime under the laws of another state or of the United States that would be a felony under this title if committed in this State;
conspiracy to commit a crime referred to in paragraphs (1) and (2) of this subsection; or
an attempt to commit a crime referred to in paragraphs (1) and (2) of this subsection.
